::DevilDuer::

Spinning around from his pursuit of CyberShark, DevilDuer watches the 
pod fall, running off in its direction and gesturing Lady Hawk and 
Hurricane to follow. It wasn't far away, and in about thirty seconds 
he jumped out into the clearing, his gun immediately aimed at Rattrap.

"Allright, you," DevilDuer says, taking a threatening step and waving 
his stun gun dangeroustly, "Get away from the pod."
